Title: Dementia 13: the animated movie

Synopsis: Eerie events leads a new wife to think she's losing her mind.

Description: Lola, a saloon dancer arrives in the town of Sant'Anna with some other dancers. The town is however terrorized by El Diablo an outlaw who wants to sell the surrounding land to the railroad company. Lola helps the colonists rebel together with Rod, a youth who has fallen in love with her.
Synopsis: Lola helps a terrorized town fight against El Diablo

Synopsis: Chuck Scott gets a job as chauffeur to tough guy Eddie Roman; but Chuck's involvement with Eddie's fearful wife becomes a nightmare.

Synopsis: Captain Scarlett saves a beautiful Princess from an arranged marriage.
